{"type":"message","id":"a7bc745c","parentId":"79596e15","timestamp":"2026-04-08T07:10:22.220Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now I understand the situation clearly:\n\n1. **舆情监控 (Weibo sentiment monitoring)**: All 7 Weibo accounts are failing because the Weibo cookies have expired. All attempts from 13:07 to 15:07 are failing with \"微博 Cookie 已失效，需要重新登录\".\n\n2. **模拟盘 (Simulated portfolio)**: The latest CSV is from 2026-04-08 but looking at the portfolio report being replied to, the simulated portfolio audit shows \"年化 55.1% | 回撤 24.9% | 夏普 2.79\" - but 张玲 says the simulated portfolio has already changed its targets. The current paper_portfolio_positions shows 21 A股 + 1 港股 + 1 ETF, but she's saying the simulation has been updated.\n\n\nI need to address both issues in my response: the Weibo cookie expiration requires re-authentication, and I should verify whether the JoinQuant simulated portfolio has been updated with new targets versus what I'm currently tracking.","thinkingSignature":"f2ce8aae6b66ee118ae59723cff01602e1ac9030e8d2f02aedef0d2277f497b2"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_uoqv67d2smh7_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"cat ~/.openclaw/workspace/research/reports/investment_research_paper_execution_push_20260408.json 2>/dev/null || cat ~/.openclaw/workspace/research/reports/investment_research_paper_execution_push_20260407.json 2>/dev/null || ls -t ~/.openclaw/workspace/research/reports/investment_research_paper_execution_push_*.json 2>/dev/null | head -3"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":7645,"output":327,"cacheRead":20136,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":28108,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775632210475,"responseId":"06253252ed863327639d1c9e3b69c5f8"}}
