{"type":"message","id":"382de756","parentId":"78b681da","timestamp":"2026-04-08T07:10:48.514Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The latest execution summary is from March 30, 2026. The simulated portfolio positions file from April 8 exists but there's no corresponding execution summary. This confirms that the simulated portfolio data has been updated (positions changed) but the strategy/execution layer hasn't been synced.\n\nNow I have the full picture:\n\n1. **舆情监控**: Weibo cookies expired - all 7 monitors failing since ~13:07 today, last successful run was before that\n2. **模拟盘**: The paper_portfolio_positions CSV was updated to April 8 (new targets), but there's no corresponding execution summary after March 30\n\n张玲 is correct on both counts. I need to:\n\n\n1. Fix the Weibo cookie issue (needs re-login)\n2. Get the latest simulated portfolio targets from JoinQuant\n\nFor the Weibo cookie, I'll need to ask the user to provide new cookies since the skill doesn't have a built-in login mechanism. For the simulated portfolio, I need to check if there's a way to pull the latest from JoinQuant. The cookie.env file has the Weibo authentication, and the monitoring script relies on it to fetch new posts.\n\nI should give 张玲 a clear status report: the Weibo cookie expired today around 13:07, so all 7 accounts went dark, and I'll need her to provide new cookies to restore monitoring. For the simulated portfolio, there's a newer position file from April 8 that hasn't been synced to the execution layer yet, so I need to figure out how to get the current targets from JoinQuant.","thinkingSignature":"e46f9a29f7f69ec4cc8a43a5baa3700ccbec7a51a33a71ff10115c53fbffa6e6"},{"type":"text","text":"[[reply_to_current]] 确认了两个问题：\n\n**1. 舆情监控 — 微博 Cookie 全部失效**\n日志显示今天 13:07 起所有 7 个博主监控全部报错：\n> `微博 Cookie 已失效，需要重新登录`\n\n每轮都在失败，最近一次是 15:07。这意味着**最近 2 小时完全没有新微博数据**。需要你重新提供微博登录 Cookie（从 weibo.com 的开发者工具里抓 `cookie:` 头的完整内容）。\n\n**2. 模拟盘 — 持仓数据已有更新**\n我本地最新的 `paper_portfolio_positions` 确实是 2026-04-08 的版本（23只持仓），但配套的 **策略执行报告只到 3月30日**，之后的调仓信号没有同步过来。\n\n请问：\n- 模拟盘是否已经在 JoinQuant 上做了新的调仓？能否截图或导出最新的持仓列表给我？\n- 微博 Cookie 需要你从浏览器重新抓，步骤：打开 weibo.com → F12 → Network → 任意请求 → 复制 Request Headers 里的 `cookie:` 整段内容发我\n\n两个问题都明确了，需要你配合提供 cookie 才能继续。"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":8331,"output":560,"cacheRead":20136,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":29027,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775632226408,"responseId":"06253262385d57d8f6828d2364ab4ee2"}}
