{"type":"message","id":"5402853b","parentId":"cb78e6e9","timestamp":"2026-04-08T07:16:23.072Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user is clarifying that the simulated portfolio (模拟盘) runs locally, not on JoinQuant. So the positions in `paper_portfolio_positions_20260408.csv` are from the local machine. The issue is that the local strategy code (小市值策略) generates signals and the local portfolio reflects those, but I don't have visibility into what the current local strategy signals are.\n\nThe user says the simulated portfolio has already changed targets. So the holdings I see from the 2026-04-08 CSV may still be the current holdings (the report was generated at 15:05 today), but the strategy execution signals after 3/30 are what I'm missing.\n \nI need to locate the local strategy code on this machine to understand what it's been running, then figure out how to connect the user's report from 4/01 with the current local portfolio state and any signals generated since the last execution summary on 3/30.","thinkingSignature":"0ca3feb98dbbcb43f0929ab83b9ac9d38dbbbb4522c0b701478ea4d4c9bdb4a6"},{"type":"text","text":"明白了，模拟盘是本地跑的。问题变成：本地那份策略（推测是聚宽适配版 Python 代码）跑在你自己机器上，我这边只有持仓快照，没有信号/调仓记录。\n\n几个问题需要你帮我确认：\n\n**持仓方面：**\n4月1日那份持仓报告（今天 15:05 生成的那份）——里面的 23 只股票，**是当前最新的本地模拟盘持仓吗**？还是说本地策略在这之后又有调仓？\n\n**策略代码方面：**\n你的小市值策略代码现在跑在你本机的哪个路径下？比如 `~/miniqmt/`、`~/joinquant/`、还是其他目录？\n\n如果你能告诉我策略的代码路径，我可以帮你：\n1. 从代码层面读出最新持仓/信号\n2. 重新生成一份带最新信号的执行报告\n3. 同步给舆情那边做一致性校验\n\n你现在本地模拟盘的最新持仓，和今天那份报告里的 23 只完全一致吗？"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":77,"output":393,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":28395,"totalTokens":28865,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775632563644,"responseId":"062533b499a581d9b69cbccc9aa5a7f2"}}
