{"type":"message","id":"4f2b6ec7","parentId":"bb77b7c1","timestamp":"2026-04-08T07:21:34.056Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now I see! The `portfolio_positions.csv` in the `config` folder shows a much larger set of holdings - this looks like the **real/live trading** portfolio (40+ stocks). This is the same as the holdings in the daily report from the user earlier. This is the REAL account (实盘).\n\nThe paper portfolio in `paper_aggressive_execution_holdings_20260408.csv` is the simulated portfolio with 10 stocks.\n\nOK so the situation is:\n- **Real account (实盘)**: 40+ stocks as shown in `portfolio_positions.csv` - this is the user's real account from THS (同花顺)\n\n\n- **Paper trading (模拟盘)**: 10 stocks in `paper_aggressive_execution_holdings_20260408.csv` as of 2026-04-08\n\nThe user's daily report showing 21 A-shares, 1 HK stock, and 1 ETF aligns with what's in `portfolio_positions.csv` - there's a slight naming difference between 588000.SH (ETF) and 511880.SH (fund), but the count is close enough that they're likely the same holdings.\n\nLooking at the paper portfolio holdings as of 2026-04-08, there are 10 stocks including 002025.SZ, 002173.SZ, 002342.SZ, and others with their respective quantities and average costs.\n\nToday the system generated 4 stop-loss sell signals and 10 buy signals, though only 2 of those buys actually went through. The real issue is that the user is pointing out the paper trading positions have shifted - the holdings file shows 002025, 002173, 002342, 002471, 300129, 300342, 300503, 301018, 603626, and 603778, which are entirely different from the previous day's positions. I need to regenerate the report with these new holdings to get an accurate view of what's actually happening.\n\nFor the sentiment monitoring piece, the Weibo cookies are expired, but I can still generate the updated paper trading report since I have today's holdings file. I'm now pulling together the complete picture: the real account from the 20260408 THS data shows 21 stocks, while the paper account has shifted to these 10 new positions with the recent trades executed today.","thinkingSignature":"99d4f92186b06e60aaa596271f37fccff9fe379e8f37f618e6734104cc4d46bf"},{"type":"text","text":"[[reply_to_current]] 找到了。找到了本地完整的模拟盘链路。\n\n## 舆情监控 + 模拟盘现状\n\n### 舆情微博 Cookie — 全部失效\n日志确认：从今天 13:07~15:37 每轮 7 个博主全部报错 `Cookie 已失效`。**最近 2 小时没有新微博推送。**\n\n需要你重新从浏览器抓 cookie：\n1. 打开 [weibo.com](https://weibo.com)\n2. F12 → Network → 随便点一个请求\n3. 找到 Request Headers 里的 `cookie:` 完整内容，粘贴给我\n\n---\n\n### 模拟盘 — 找到了，已换标的\n\n路径：`~/.openclaw/workspace/quant_projects/personal-a-share-research-system/`\n\n**今日持仓（2026-04-08，共 10 只）：**\n\n| 代码 | 名称 | 数量 | 成本 |\n|------|------|------|------|\n| 002025.SZ | 航天电器 | 3,600 | 60.12 |\n| 002173.SZ | 创新医疗 | 4,100 | 29.63 |\n| 002342.SZ | 巨力索具 | 7,700 | 14.41 |\n| 002471.SZ | 科陆电子 | 17,500 | 9.18 |\n| 300129.SZ | 泰胜风能 | 19,700 | 15.15 |\n| 300342.SZ | 天银机电 | 400 | 46.98 |\n| 300503.SZ | 昊志机电 | 2,100 | 52.08 |\n| 301018.SZ | 隆盛科技 | 2,800 | 102.58 |\n| 603626.SH | 科森科技 | 6,400 | 23.32 |\n| 603778.SH | 乾景园林 | 6,800 | 22.02 |\n\n**今日信号（同步到 11:56）：**\n- **止损卖出 4 只**：002173(-19%)、002342(-11%)、300129(-22%)、301018(-14%)\n- **买入信号 10 只**，其中 2 只通过风控：002222(80.76元)、301550(166.50元)，其余 8 只因超出单票 15 万预算被 block\n\n这个和你的实盘（23 只券商账户）**完全不一样**，确实是两套独立组合。微博 cookie 搞定之后我可以同步更新舆情监控配置。"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":23665,"output":1020,"cacheRead":20037,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":44722,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775632862009,"responseId":"062534dea4f500737c22a6364290c58b"}}
